<div class="card-entry-module__heading">

    <h2 class="card-entry_header">
        Makeup Make Change
        </h2>


            <p class="card-entry__heading-content">
                We make makeup. We&rsquo;re also committed to making change to help create a better world. Learn about our global initiatives and discover how we can drive real change together.<br />
<br />
<strong>Our 2024 brand impact report is available. Please read it <a href="/-/media/project/loreal/brand-sites/mny/americas/us/about-us/mny-impactreport-2024_final_v2.pdf?rev=b110e9c4b48f4f9fb7dddf0cc5bc22f3&amp;hash=451D8C1FA61F75834DEE5F2AD71BFA36" target="_blank">here</a>.</strong><br />
You can also consult our 2022 brand impact report <a href="/-/media/project/loreal/brand-sites/mny/americas/us/homepage/home-entry-card-folder/maybelline_impact_report_2022.pdf?rev=4a5ebe86048941b18ecac3ab319ed47d&amp;hash=4C0C69DEEC68102591D72BD9BD7B7425" target="_blank">here</a>.
            </p>



</div>
